docs.text: /* Application header should be static for the landing page */ .md-header { position: initial; } /* Remove spacing, as we cannot hide it completely */ .md-main__inner { margin: 0; } /* Hide main content for now */ .md-content { display: none; } /* Hide table of contents */ @media screen and (min-width: 60em) { .md-sidebar--secondary { display: none; } } /* Hide navigation */ @media screen and (min-width: 76.25em) { .md-sidebar--primary { display: none; } } body { background-image: url(./images/wallpaper.jpg); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: fixed; background-size: cover; }
